Maintainer: Keren Zhang <keren.zhang@utoronto.ca>
Description: The CancerMutAnalyzer is an R package for enhancing the analysis 
of cancer mutation data by providing tools for data extraction, filtering, 
sequence analysis, and visualization to help researchers identify mutation 
patterns and genomic signatures.
